					(size 1.27 1.27)
				)
				(hide yes)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "WM8960 stereo audio codec. AVDD/DCVDD = 3.3V (separate rails recommended), each with 10uF + 100nF decoupling. REFGND requires a 1uF cap to GND (handled internally to this block). I2C address 0x1A. I2S in slave mode. On-board class-D bridge-tied speaker amp drives SPK_LP/LN and SPK_RP/RN to 4-8 ohm speakers; do not common any output. MIC_BIAS supplies 0.65*AVDD to electret microphones."
			(at 368.3 76.2 0)
			(effects
				(font
					(size 1.27 1.27)
				)
				(hide yes)
			)
		)
