		(property "Description" "Decoupling network on 3V3: 4 x 100nF MLCC ceramic (one per IC supply pin), one 10uF bulk capacitor. All return to GND. Place 100nF caps directly at IC power pins; place bulk near the regulator output / supply entry. Net name on RAIL pin is \"3V3\"."
			(at 76.2 76.2 0)
